I got in my first car accident ever today.&nbsp; The stupid&nbsp;weather made my car swerve back and forth.&nbsp; So, I tried to pull my car off the road so that&nbsp;I wouldn't hit&nbsp;anyone and&nbsp;I ended up running right over a sign.&nbsp; This&nbsp;was the scariest time of my life.&nbsp; I'm kinda scared to drive now. I had to drive my car home today and&nbsp;I went 30mph the whole way home.&nbsp; I tried going faster but the I just got paranoid that something would happen, so&nbsp;I slowed down.&nbsp;

I fucking hate snow.&nbsp;&nbsp;


Jess-

California, baby, here we come!&nbsp;
